								<h1 class="post-title single">Is It Time for Civics to Make a Comeback?</h1>

								<div class="meta single">

	<span class="meta-author">
		<a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/mindshift/author/hollykorbey/" title="Posts by Holly Korbey" rel="author">Holly Korbey</a> | 
	</span> 

	<span class="meta-date">
		August 1, 2013	</span> 

