		 | <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/mindshift/2013/08/is-it-time-for-civics-to-make-a-comeback/#comments" rel="bookmark" title="Comments for Is It Time for Civics to Make a Comeback?"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="30053 http://blogs.kqed.org/mindshift/?p=30053">2 Comments</span></a>
	</span>
	 

</div>
